Updates an existing conference provider's settings

Source: R/alexaforbusiness_operations.R
alexaforbusiness_update_conference_provider.Rd

Updates an existing conference provider's settings.

alexaforbusiness_update_conference_provider(ConferenceProviderArn,
  ConferenceProviderType, IPDialIn, PSTNDialIn, MeetingSetting)

Arguments

ConferenceProviderArn

[required] The ARN of the conference provider.
ConferenceProviderType

[required] The type of the conference provider.
IPDialIn

The IP endpoint and protocol for calling.
PSTNDialIn

The information for PSTN conferencing.
MeetingSetting

[required] The meeting settings for the conference provider.

Request syntax

svc$update_conference_provider(
  ConferenceProviderArn = "string",
  ConferenceProviderType = "CHIME"|"BLUEJEANS"|"FUZE"|"GOOGLE_HANGOUTS"|"POLYCOM"|"RINGCENTRAL"|"SKYPE_FOR_BUSINESS"|"WEBEX"|"ZOOM"|"CUSTOM",
  IPDialIn = list(
    Endpoint = "string",
    CommsProtocol = "SIP"|"SIPS"|"H323"
  ),
  PSTNDialIn = list(
    CountryCode = "string",
    PhoneNumber = "string",
    OneClickIdDelay = "string",
    OneClickPinDelay = "string"
  ),
  MeetingSetting = list(
    RequirePin = "YES"|"NO"|"OPTIONAL"
  )
)
